Dear Member, 
 Your information requires an important update as soon as possible. You're receiving this message 
 due to errors encountered in our verification process of Online DMV Records as at July, 15 2021. 
 This might be due to one of the following reasons: 
  
Incomplete verification process  
Your information has changed or incomplete 
 We advise you to complete the update process swiftly as it takes less than 3 minutes to complete. 
 Click here to update your records. 
 Thank you. 
 Illinois Department of Information
